%sql
-- player랑 해보자
-- 그럼 플레이어의 경기당 frequency
-- match_id|player_slot|account_id|assists|deaths|denies|gold|gold_per_min|gold_spent|hero_damage|hero_healing|hero_id|kills|level|pings|isRadiant|win|lose|kda
SELECT  m.match_id, p.player_slot, sum(frequency), p.assists ,p.deaths,p.denies,p.gold,p.gold_per_min,p.gold_spent,p.hero_damage,p.hero_healing,p.hero_id,p.kills,p.level,p.pings,p.isRadiant,p.win,p.lose,p.kda, m.duration,
FROM 

(select match_id, (CASE  
WHEN player_slot <5 THEN True  
ELSE False 
END ) isRadiant, player_slot, sum(count) as frequency
from dotachat group by match_id,player_slot, isRadiant order by match_id) c

join dotaplayers p on c.match_id=p.match_id and c.player_slot=p.player_slot join dotamatches m on p.match_id=m.match_id group by m.match_id, p.player_slot,p.assists ,p.deaths,p.denies,p.gold,p.gold_per_min,p.gold_spent,p.hero_damage,p.hero_healing,p.hero_id,p.kills,p.level,p.pings,p.isRadiant,p.win,p.lose,p.kda

%sql
-- match_id|match_seq_num|radiant_win|start_time|duration|tower_status_radiant|tower_status_dire|barracks_status_radiant|barracks_status_dire|first_blood_time
SELECT  m.match_id,  c.isRadiant ,avg(c.frequency), sum(c.frequency),m.radiant_win,m.start_time, m.duration, m.first_blood_time,
(CASE  

WHEN m.radiant_win = True and c.isRadiant= True THEN 1  
WHEN m.radiant_win = True and c.isRadiant= False THEN 0  
WHEN m.radiant_win = False and c.isRadiant= True THEN 0  

ELSE 1 

END ) is_win
FROM 
	(select match_id, (CASE  
	WHEN player_slot <5 THEN True  
	ELSE False 
	END ) isRadiant, sum(count) as frequency
	from dotachat group by match_id, isRadiant) c 
	JOIN dotamatches m on c.match_id=m.match_id group by m.match_id,  c.isRadiant , m.radiant_win, m.radiant_win,m.start_time, m.duration, m.first_blood_time
-- Select * from dotachat limit 20
